duties_responsibilities.duty: Schedule appointments for sales teams, both in-person and virtual, with a goal of 18-25 appointments per week. Requires good communication and organizational skills.
Support sales teams with expense reports, including review, submission, and processing of check requests for meeting reimbursement and charitable contributions.
Additional tasks include ordering literature for meetings, updating meeting notes in CRM, coordinating conference calls, and aggregating team success stories for reporting to leadership.
